data.description: Enormous money making potential! While this nearly 17 1/2 acre LAKE FRONT PROPERTY with 2 ponds would make a picturesque setting for you to build your dream home, it also has huge commercial potential! Owner had plans to finish out a 200 site campground on the lake (which could earn you your investment back in less than 2 years)! This property has tons of room, cleared and bushhogged flat land, a 3 bed 2 bath home with a brand new roof, a second storage home, barns, carport, storage buildings, huge metal building with workshop, a livestock pond, a stocked pond with a dock, side-by-side/4wheeler trails, 6 campers included (that all already have long term renters), gravel access roads, AND THE LAKE, it's all right there, just waiting for your dreams! Potential everywhere you look - you do not want to miss this!
